snippet.title: APSULOV: End of Gods - Alpha Trailer 1 (2018)
snippet.description:
A Future, Viking, Horror, Adventure game
Apsulov: End of Gods

WISHLIST TODAY!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/960980/Apsulov_End_of_Gods/
Release: Q3 2019

APSULOV is a first person dark adventure/horror game where Nordic creatures and
gods are combined with science and technology to create a horrifying new world!

Being created by Angry Demon Studio
